# ExpenseIQ 💸

A modern, dark-themed expense tracker web app built with vanilla JavaScript, HTML and CSS. Track your income, expenses, and budget goals with real-time visual feedback.

> 🔗 > **Live Demo:** [ExpenseIQ](https://97chopra.github.io/Expense_Tracker/)
---

## 📸 Preview

![ExpenseIQ Screenshot](preview.png)

---

## ✨ Features

- 📊 **Spending Breakdown** — Live donut chart showing expenses by category
- 💳 **Transaction Management** — Add, view and delete income & expenses
- 🎯 **Budget Goals** — Progress bars that warn when nearing or exceeding limits
- 🔍 **Search & Filter** — Filter by category or search by name instantly
- 💾 **localStorage Persistence** — Data stays saved after browser refresh
- 📥 **CSV Export** — Download all transactions as a spreadsheet
- 📱 **Responsive Design** — Works on desktop and mobile
- 🌙 **Dark Dashboard Theme** — Professional fintech-inspired UI

---

## 🛠️ Built With

| Technology | Purpose |
|---|---|
| HTML5 | Structure and layout |
| CSS3 | Dark theme styling, animations, responsive design |
| JavaScript (ES6+) | App logic, localStorage, DOM manipulation |
| Chart.js | Interactive donut chart |

